  "description": "This compilation includes 2 games:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Miner\">Miner</a> - is a game loosely based on the TV game show named Wheel of Fortune. The players take turns guessing the consonants or the vowels to form a word or a saying. The game allows to play up to three human or computer players. Each turn begins with the wheel spin. The game features 3 elimination rounds and finals.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Ko%c5%82o+Szcz%c4%99%c5%9bcia\">Ko?o Szcz??cia</a> - is a timed <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Minesweeper\">Minesweeper</a> clone with sci-fi background story. The gameplay rules remain unchanged. Selected dot shows the number of bombs in the neighborhood. The detected mine may be marked with a flag, although number of flags is limited.</li></ul>",
